{
  "stem": "13673.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 259.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was organized by the Jewish community throughout Germany and Austria, Czechoslovakia and Poland as well, a few in Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also not only Jewish, but Christian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of Quakers were involved with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were going to be taken to England.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was a, a tremendous undertaking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In England, they had to pass an act of Parliament to get the funding to-- and, and to get people to take us in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was just--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were private families that would take us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were institutions that would take us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them were very Orthodox Jewish organizations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Others were-- it was the whole spectrum.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't have to be Jewish at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I-- after my first-- I'm jumping the gun-- but after my first experience with a Jewish family, I, I was living with Christian people all along-- the rest of the time that I was in England.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm jumping ahead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She, she had to just put my name on a list.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whether she paid any money for this, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She-- I know that that wasn't the requirement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You didn't have to pay for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But since we were well off, I, I wouldn't be surprised if she did contribute to it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, she-- of course, she had to prepare me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, I was a little girl, and she had to--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--get me used to it. 11.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she got a teacher in to teach me some English, and that's number one, I guess.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I learned to say, the dog is under the table.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also, there were things to pack, what I could take.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Too much, actually.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of the stuff I never saw anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
